'''盾牌-南十字臂'''，也稱為'''盾牌-半人馬臂'''，是從[[銀河系|銀河系]]中心接近[[棒旋星系|棒]]的末端，由瀰散的氣體和塵埃組成，向外螺旋彎曲的長串[[恆星|星流]]。儘管自20世紀50年代以來，沒有確實強而有力的證據，但銀河系一直被認為有4條[[螺旋星系#螺旋臂|螺旋臂]]<ref name=bash>{{Cite journal | last1 = Bash | first1 = F. N. | doi = 10.1086/159401 | title = Does the Galaxy have four spiral arms | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 250 | pages = 551 | year = 1981 | pmid =  | pmc = | bibcode = 1981ApJ...250..551B }}</ref>。在2008年，利用[[史匹哲太空望遠鏡|史匹哲太空望遠鏡]]觀測的資料，在[[人馬臂|船底-人馬臂]]和[[天鵝臂|矩尺臂]]的[[紅群聚|紅群聚]]沒有如預期的密度<ref name=benjamin>{{Cite journal | display-authors=1| last1 = Churchwell | first1 = E. | last2 = Babler | first2 = B. L. | last3 = Meade | first3 = M. R. | last4 = Whitney | first4 = B. A. | last5 = Benjamin | first5 = R. | last6 = Indebetouw | first6 = R. | last7 = Cyganowski | first7 = C. | last8 = Robitaille | first8 = T. P. | last9 = Povich | first9 = M. | doi = 10.1086/597811 | title = The Spitzer/GLIMPSE surveys: a new view of the Milky Way | journal = Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific | volume = 121 | issue = 877 | pages = 213 | year = 2009 | bibcode=2009PASP..121..213C| pmid =  | pmc = }}</ref>。在2014年，一項為期12年，研究大質量恆星的分布和壽命<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Urquhart | first1 = J. S. | last2 = Figura | first2 = C. C. | last3 = Moore | first3 = T. J. T. | last4 = Hoare | first4 = M. G. | last5 = Lumsden | first5 = S. L. | last6 = Mottram | first6 = J. C. | last7 = Thompson | first7 = M. A. | last8 = Oudmaijer | first8 = R. D. | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stt2006 | title = The RMS survey: Galactic distribution of massive star formation | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 437 | issue = 2 | pages = 1791 | year = 2013 | pmid =  | pmc = | bibcode = 2014MNRAS.437.1791U |arxiv = 1310.4758 }}</ref>，以及對邁射和疏散星團分布的研究<ref name=bobylev>{{Cite journal | last1 = Bobylev | first1 = V. V. | last2 = Bajkova | first2 = A. T. | title = The Milky Way spiral structure parameters from data on masers and selected open clusters | doi = 10.1093/mnras/stt1987 | journal = Monthly Notices of the Royal Astronomical Society | volume = 437 | issue = 2 | pages = 1549 | year = 2013 | pmid =  | pmc = | bibcode = 2014MNRAS.437.1549B |arxiv = 1310.3974 }}</ref>，兩者都發現4條螺旋臂的證據。

盾牌-半人馬臂位於小船底-人馬臂和主要的[[英仙臂|英仙臂]]之間。盾牌-半人馬臂開始的位置靠近''盾牌臂''的核心，然後逐漸變成''半人馬臂''<ref name=Churchwell2009>{{cite journal|last=Churchwell|first=Ed|author2=Babler, Brian L.|author3=Meade, Marlin A.|title=The Spitzer/GLIMPSE Surveys: A New View of the Milky Way|journal=Publications of the Astronomical Society of the Pacific|year=2009|volume=121|issue=877|pages=213–230|doi=10.1086/597811|url=http://www.astro.wisc.edu/sirtf/Churchwell_2009.pdf|format=pdf|bibcode=2009PASP..121..213C|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2014-01-21|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Mn3zcVjn?url=http://www.astro.wisc.edu/sirtf/Churchwell_2009.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

盾牌-半人馬臂與銀河的棒連接的區域是豐富的[[恆星形成|恆星形成區]]。2006年在那兒發現一大群新恆星，其中包括有14顆[[紅超巨星|紅超巨星]]命名為[[RSGC1|RSGC1]]的集團。在2007年發現距離RSGC1只有幾百光年，擁有5,000顆新形成恆星，命名為[[史蒂芬森2|RSGC2]]的集團。估計它的年齡還不到2,000萬年，並有26顆紅超巨星，是已知此種恆星的最大集團<ref name=davies>>{{Cite journal | last1 = Davies | first1 = B. | last2 = Figer | first2 = D. F. | last3 = Kudritzki | first3 = R. P. | last4 = MacKenty | first4 = J. | last5 = Najarro | first5 = F. | last6 = Herrero | first6 = A. | doi = 10.1086/522224 | title = A Massive Cluster of Red Supergiants at the Base of the Scutum‐Crux Arm | journal = The Astrophysical Journal | volume = 671 | pages = 781 | year = 2007 | pmid =  | pmc =| format = pdf | bibcode=2007ApJ...671..781D|arxiv = 0708.0821 }}</ref>。這個區域的恆星集團還有[[紅超巨星團3|紅超巨星團3]]和[[阿利坎特8|阿利坎特8]]<ref name=Negueruela2010>{{Cite journal | volume = 513 | journal = Astronomy and Astrophysics | title = Another cluster of red supergiants close to RSGC1 | pages = A74 | year = 2010| bibcode = 2010A&A...513A..74N | doi = 10.1051/0004-6361/200913373 | first5 = S. | last5 = Martínez-Núñez | first2 = C. | last2 = González-Fernández | first1 = I. | last3 = Marco | first3 = A. | first4 = J. S. | last4 = Clark | last1 = Negueruela|arxiv = 1002.1823 }}</ref>。

